# Ignore node_modules at every level (root AND workspace packages). A bare
# "node_modules/" only matches the context root, which lets stale per-package
# node_modules (with host-specific pnpm symlinks) leak into the image and
# shadow the clean `pnpm install` performed inside the build stage.
**/node_modules/
# Likewise ignore build output at every level
**/dist/
.git/
.env
.env.local
*.log
coverage/
.turbo/
